OL,6,FThe ice hockey world will pay tribute
OL,7,Fto Adam Johnson this weekend - a year
OL,8,Fafter his death during a match.
OL,10,FFans, players and staff will take part
OL,11,Fin a 47-second applause before games
OL,12,Fin the Elite Ice Hockey League (EIHL).
OL,14,FJohnson, who was 29, wore the number
OL,15,F47 on his back for Nottingham Panthers.
OL,17,FThe EIHL said in a statement: "We
OL,18,Fwould also like to actively encourage
OL,19,Ffurther fan-led tributes before,
OL,20,Fduring or after games.
