OL,6,F"Some fans may find the applause
OL,7,Fdifficult, and we ask that you
OL,8,Fcontinue to support each other as you
OL,9,Fdid so wonderfully over the past year."
OL,11,FJohnson died after his neck was cut in
OL,12,Fa collision with a Sheffield Steelers
OL,13,Fplayer during a match in Sheffield on
OL,14,F28 October 2023.
OL,16,FHis death was witnessed by thousands
OL,17,Fof fans inside the Sheffield Utilita
OL,18,FArena.
