OL,6,FIn a statement, Nottingham Panthers,
OL,7,Fwho play Manchester Storm on Sunday,
OL,8,Fasked supporters to lay flowers
OL,9,Funderneath a plaque installed in
OL,10,Fmemory of Johnson at the Motorpoint
OL,11,FArena.
OL,13,FThe statement said: "Adam, our number
OL,14,F47, was not only an outstanding ice
OL,15,Fhockey player, but also a great team-
OL,16,Fmate and an incredible person. The
OL,17,Fclub will never ever forget him.
